{"lemma":"تَبْصِرَةٍ","slug":"تَبْصِرَةٍ","root":"ب.ص.ر","root_slug":"ب-ص-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ص-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"تَبْصِرَة","root":"بصر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2639"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%B5%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2639","headword_ar":"تبصّرهُ","root":"bSr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He looked at it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a thing: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"looked long at it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"glanced lightly at it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramaqahu","text_ar":"رَمَقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavoured, to see it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"or i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboSarahu","text_ar":"اَبْصَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in a sense explained above; see 4. (M.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabaS~aro liY fulaAnFA","text_ar":"تَبَصَّرْ لِى فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Consider thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"examine thou, for me, such a one, that thou mayest obtain a clear knowledge of him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbS~r fiY $aYo'K","text_ar":"تبصّر فِى شَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He considered a thing, endeavouring to obtain a clear knowledge of it; he looked into it, considered it, examined it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"studied it, repeatedly, until he knew it: he sought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sought leisurely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repeatedly, after the knowledge of it, until he knew it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * K, * TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbS~r fiY raA^oyihi","text_ar":"تبصّر فِى رَاْيِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi","text_ar":"فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstbSr","text_ar":"استبصر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endeavoured, to see,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discover, what would happen to him, of good and evil."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}